title: 325: Mind Pump Past, Present & Future
description: Every once in a while Sal, Adam & Justin like to free-form the entire episode and this is one of them. They talk about a little Mind Pump history, what is currently going on and a bit of the Mind Pump vision for the future. Get MAPS Anabolic, MAPS Performance, MAPS Aesthetic and the Butt Builder Blueprint (The RGB Super Bundle) packaged together at a substantial DISCOUNT at www.mindpumpmedia.com. Please subscribe, rate and review this show! Each week our favorite reviewers are announced on the show and sent Mind Pump T-shirts!
